type: Tutorial Step - Make sure You’re Comfortable

definition.text: Before you jump into governance, it’s important you know how Superalgos works!

paragraphs.text: We have got a lot of exciting things to talk about, but I want to make sure you can follow along easily.
If you haven't already, make sure you go through the Getting Started Tutorials before continuing!
No need to be an expert, but you will need some general knowledge of the system to understand what this is all about!
